      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CLARICE (3) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 1.5 lengths from the winner Hurry Up Eric (27.64) at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Good form should continue. HUM BUG MONELLI (2) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at Cannington over 520m behind Speed Cheller (31.03) in a Novice race. Placed at her previous run. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Great chance to atone. GOOD TOWN (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (28.17) in a Novice race at this track. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Worth another chance. AUREATE (8) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
